1
00:00:12,258 --> 00:00:18,465
{\an5}If only I knew where
their souls were now,
I'd be able to save
Neji and the others...

2
00:00:19,533 --> 00:00:20,300
{\an1}<i>[Shino Collapsing]</i>

3
00:00:20,334 --> 00:00:21,369
{\an3}[gasp]

4
00:00:21,903 --> 00:00:24,339
Shino! No!

5
00:00:24,372 --> 00:00:25,473
[grunts in pain]

6
00:00:25,507 --> 00:00:27,375
{\an1}Shino! Are
you okay!?

7
00:00:27,409 --> 00:00:31,681
{\an1}<i>...please, stop!</i>
<i>You're a true asset to</i>
<i>our military strength!</i>

8
00:00:31,714 --> 00:00:33,249
{\an1}<i>...we can't afford</i>
<i> to lose you!</i>

9
00:00:33,282 --> 00:00:35,952
Shino, please
listen to reason!

10
00:00:35,986 --> 00:00:39,289
I will not give
up, Hinata.

11
00:00:39,322 --> 00:00:40,857
But, Shino, you...

12
00:00:40,891 --> 00:00:45,462
{\an1}We're just one step from
saving Neji and Kiba...
I cannot stop.

13
00:00:46,064 --> 00:00:52,905
{\an4}The reason is because if
I do before we can even
reach them, the flame of
hope will be extinguished!

14
00:00:54,272 --> 00:00:56,307
{\an1}We can't give up!

15
00:00:56,341 --> 00:01:01,114
{\an4}If the only was to save them
is to find out where they are,
then we'll keep searching
for them until we do...

16
00:01:03,116 --> 00:01:04,751
I won't quit...

17
00:01:06,453 --> 00:01:08,022
[small gasp]

18
00:01:20,669 --> 00:01:25,741
{\an1}Shikaku, are you there?
Are Shikamaru and the
others still okay?

19
00:01:25,774 --> 00:01:29,579
{\an1}A little while ago,
I suddenly stopped
sensing their chakra!

20
00:01:29,612 --> 00:01:31,681
{\an1}If there's anything
I can do, tell me!

21
00:01:33,516 --> 00:01:36,352
<i>(Naruto)</i>
<i>Hey! Say </i>
<i>something!</i>

22
00:01:36,385 --> 00:01:38,454
Shikaku...

23
00:01:38,489 --> 00:01:40,591
{\an1}Hmm.

24
00:01:41,625 --> 00:01:43,995
{\an1}All right. Connect
me to Naruto.

25
00:01:47,565 --> 00:01:50,301
{\an1}<i>(Shikaku)</i>
<i>Naruto, can </i>
<i>you hear me?</i>

26
00:01:50,335 --> 00:01:53,239
<i>(Naruto)</i>
<i>Shikaku, what's</i>
<i>going on!?</i>

27
00:01:53,271 --> 00:01:55,340
<i>What happened to</i>
<i>Shikamaru and the</i>
<i>others!?</i>

28
00:01:56,341 --> 00:02:00,713
{\an7}<i>(Telepathically)</i>
<i>We're not entirely</i>
<i>sure, but we know the</i>
<i>jutsu the enemy used.</i>

29
00:02:00,746 --> 00:02:03,650
{\an7}<i>It's called the</i>
<i>Underworld Transfer</i>
<i>Jutsu...</i>

30
00:02:03,683 --> 00:02:07,287
{\an4}<i>(Shikaku)</i>
<i>It extracts the soul</i>
<i>from a victim and places</i>
<i>it into a special barrier.</i>

31
00:02:07,320 --> 00:02:09,389
Seriously!? It
extracts their soul?

32
00:02:09,422 --> 00:02:12,392
{\an4}Yeah, but... they're all
still alive, aren't they?
We can just track down
their souls and save them!

33
00:02:12,425 --> 00:02:14,929
We can just track
down their souls
and save them!

34
00:02:14,962 --> 00:02:17,166
{\an1}Unfortunately,
that's impossible.

35
00:02:17,199 --> 00:02:19,902
{\an1}There's no shinobi
with the ability
to locate souls.

36
00:02:19,935 --> 00:02:22,504
So, what do you
need me to do?

37
00:02:22,538 --> 00:02:28,244
{\an4}Right now, Naruto, you're
the only shinobi who can
mitigate the chaos within
the Allied Shinobi Forces.

38
00:02:28,278 --> 00:02:33,349
{\an4}You may have immense
reserves of chakra, but
there's no way you can
cover every battlefield.

39
00:02:33,383 --> 00:02:36,619
{\an1}Even as it is,
you're stretching
yourself too thin.

40
00:02:36,653 --> 00:02:38,622
{\an1}We've now reached
a critical point:

41
00:02:39,089 --> 00:02:44,162
{\an7}The Allied Forces can't
spare a vital asset like
you, not for just four
shinobi.

42
00:02:44,196 --> 00:02:45,596
{\an8}What!? Don't
be an idiot!

43
00:02:45,629 --> 00:02:49,768
{\an8}They're not just
shinobi! I mean,
Shikamaru is your
own son!

44
00:02:49,801 --> 00:02:54,941
{\an8}And that's not all! I
heard Shino and Ino are
desperately trying to
save them--!

45
00:02:54,974 --> 00:02:57,310
{\an8}<i>(Naruto)</i>
<i>How can you turn your</i>
<i>back on all of them!?</i>

46
00:02:57,342 --> 00:03:01,949
{\an7}<i>As our chief strategist,</i>
<i>I must coordinate every</i>
<i>one's actions.</i>

47
00:03:01,982 --> 00:03:04,284
{\an7}<i>I cannot allow</i>
<i>people to go off</i>
<i>on their own.</i>

48
00:03:04,584 --> 00:03:08,989
{\an7}<i>Your duty right now</i>
<i>is to identify the </i>
<i>enemy by sensing </i>
<i>their malice.</i>

49
00:03:09,022 --> 00:03:11,926
{\an7}<i>You must focus on</i>
<i>doing your very</i>
<i>best in that role.</i>

50
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:13,228
{\an8}Come on! Give
me a break!

51
00:03:13,261 --> 00:03:14,629
{\an8}<i>(Inoichi)</i>
<i>Naruto!</i>
[gasp]

52
00:03:14,662 --> 00:03:18,399
{\an8}Shikaku's right.
You must put all
your efforts into
your mission.

53
00:03:18,433 --> 00:03:19,969
{\an8}Got it!?

54
00:03:28,879 --> 00:03:31,681
Roger that!
I'm on it!

55
00:03:32,015 --> 00:03:34,017
{\an3}Hm.

56
00:05:29,712 --> 00:05:31,547
{\an1}[laugh] Give it up!

57
00:05:31,581 --> 00:05:34,551
{\an1}<i>LIke I said earlier,</i>
<i>we're immortal...</i>

58
00:05:34,585 --> 00:05:39,190
{\an5}(Tayuya)
And even if you losers could
defeat us, it still wouldn't
make this barrier come down!

59
00:05:39,224 --> 00:05:42,260
{\an1}Ha! Face it! There's
nothing you can do!

60
00:05:44,662 --> 00:05:45,864
Huh?

61
00:05:51,471 --> 00:05:52,605
{\an1}Hm.

62
00:05:55,808 --> 00:05:57,344
Heh.

63
00:06:00,414 --> 00:06:03,650
What an idiot!
You're wide open!

64
00:06:11,059 --> 00:06:13,228
Eight Trigrams!
Air Palm!

65
00:06:14,762 --> 00:06:15,731
[grunt]

66
00:06:21,438 --> 00:06:23,473
[♪ flute music]

67
00:06:23,973 --> 00:06:25,543
Fang Over Fang!

68
00:06:34,385 --> 00:06:36,787
[gasp]

69
00:06:38,889 --> 00:06:40,425
[gasp]

70
00:06:52,171 --> 00:06:53,606
Huh?

71
00:06:59,880 --> 00:07:03,284
[♪ flute music]

72
00:07:03,318 --> 00:07:08,323
{\an7}<i>That's it! Eat up all</i>
<i>his chakra so that he</i>
<i>can never get back on</i>
<i>his feet!</i>

73
00:07:11,693 --> 00:07:12,495
Ahh!

74
00:07:14,463 --> 00:07:16,232
Now, Sakon!

75
00:07:18,634 --> 00:07:20,236
{\an7}<i>Shadow Pull Jutsu!</i>

76
00:07:20,936 --> 00:07:21,837
Ahhh!

77
00:07:30,348 --> 00:07:32,850
{\an1}That fool! What
is he doing!?

78
00:07:32,884 --> 00:07:34,685
Yes! It worked!

79
00:07:34,719 --> 00:07:39,391
{\an4}That gate is enormous.
So I wondered what would
happen if its foundation
were weakened...

80
00:07:39,424 --> 00:07:40,926
<i>I was right!</i>

81
00:07:42,261 --> 00:07:45,998
{\an1}Why you jerk! You
tricked us into
attacking that spot!

82
00:07:46,031 --> 00:07:48,800
{\an1}That's what you were
after all along!

83
00:07:53,273 --> 00:07:55,543
{\an1}Damn! You bastards!

84
00:08:01,682 --> 00:08:07,522
{\an4}"We're trapped," "We have
no hope of escape?" You really
think anything like that
would make us give up?

85
00:08:07,556 --> 00:08:11,993
{\an1}Don't underestimate
us, you piece of crap!

86
00:08:12,461 --> 00:08:16,165
{\an1}Actually, you're the ones
who are underestimating us!

87
00:08:16,199 --> 00:08:19,402
{\an1}I could've sworn that
you were stronger the
last time we faced off.

88
00:08:19,435 --> 00:08:25,175
{\an1}Well then, you think that
means all of <i>us</i> have improved
but you guys stayed the same?

89
00:08:25,209 --> 00:08:26,877
<i>(Kiba)</i>
<i>Sounds right to me!</i>

90
00:08:26,910 --> 00:08:27,811
<i>(Akamaru)</i>
<i>[bark]</i>

91
00:08:27,844 --> 00:08:30,214
{\an1}I'm gonna shut that
big mouth of yours!

92
00:08:30,248 --> 00:08:34,619
{\an5}Listen, Shikamaru...
Does it really seem
wise to rile them up
like this?

93
00:08:36,254 --> 00:08:42,727
{\an4}You know, come to think of it.
You & all the other reanimations
were called back to become tools
of war, weren't you..?

94
00:08:42,760 --> 00:08:46,633
<i>(Shikamaru)</i>
<i>So what's with your ridiculous</i>
<i>obsession about getting revenge?</i>

95
00:08:46,666 --> 00:08:50,237
{\an1}<i>And why are you directing</i>
<i>it all at us, anyway?</i>

96
00:08:50,270 --> 00:08:52,673
<i>Didn't the Sang</i>
<i>Siblings kill some</i>
<i>of you, too?</i>

97
00:08:53,340 --> 00:08:58,878
{\an1}What? We're "tools of
war?" Is that what you
called us? [laugh]

98
00:08:58,912 --> 00:09:00,147
Huh?!

99
00:09:00,181 --> 00:09:02,516
<i>(Jirobo)</i>
<i>[derisive laughter]</i>

100
00:09:02,551 --> 00:09:06,754
{\an5}You ignorant fool!
We have nothing to
do whatsoever with
this war!

101
00:09:06,787 --> 00:09:11,494
{\an4}Our reanimation is
simply because of
our loyalty to Lord
Orochimaru!

102
00:09:13,429 --> 00:09:17,467
{\an1}He made us a promise
long ago, and this is
the result of that!

103
00:09:17,500 --> 00:09:26,844
[fighting]

104
00:09:26,877 --> 00:09:29,447
Yes. That's it.
Kill each other off.

105
00:09:29,481 --> 00:09:34,085
{\an1}And if you're not taking
this battle seriously, then
I'll just kill you myself!

106
00:09:37,989 --> 00:09:41,560
{\an1}[panting breaths]

107
00:09:41,594 --> 00:09:46,533
{\an5}<i>(Orochimaru)</i>
<i>The feeling that's born</i>
<i>when one transcends the</i>
<i>dear of death...</i>

108
00:09:46,566 --> 00:09:50,370
{\an5}Yes, that's it.
That's what I
wanted to bring
out in you...

109
00:09:50,404 --> 00:09:53,940
{\an1}Just look at those
fine eyes of yours...

110
00:09:53,974 --> 00:09:57,412
<i>(Orochimaru)</i>
<i>Now I shall bestow upon</i>
<i>you even greater power...</i>

111
00:09:57,445 --> 00:10:02,550
{\an1}<i>And you shall carry</i>
<i>out my bidding... as</i>
<i>my favored ones...</i>

112
00:10:03,885 --> 00:10:06,921
{\an4}<i>(Jirobo / Tayuya </i>
<i>Sakon / Kidomaru)</i>
<i>Ninja Art! Four Flames</i>
<i>Formation!</i>

113
00:10:07,423 --> 00:10:12,161
{\an5}<i>(Sakon)</i>
<i>Standing at Lord</i>
<i>Orochimaru's side, we've</i>
<i>been witness to many jutsu...</i>

114
00:10:12,194 --> 00:10:18,902
{\an1}<i>But the ultimate is...</i>
<i>The Reanimation Jutsu!</i>

115
00:10:19,737 --> 00:10:25,543
(struggling breaths)
That old geezer...
How dare he!?

116
00:10:25,576 --> 00:10:29,013
[labored breaths]

117
00:10:29,046 --> 00:10:31,882
What? Do you have
something to say?

118
00:10:31,916 --> 00:10:33,084
{\an1}No...

119
00:10:34,786 --> 00:10:38,957
In the condition I'm
in now, you four might
be able to kill me.

120
00:10:38,990 --> 00:10:41,993
This is your chance
if you dare to try...

121
00:10:44,931 --> 00:10:52,806
{\an4}Well, it seems that as long
as the Curse Mark binds you,
you cannot bring yourself to
raise your blade against me.

122
00:10:52,840 --> 00:10:58,912
{\an4}Although the attempt
failed, you did make
yourselves useful in the
attack on the Hidden Leaf.

123
00:10:59,514 --> 00:11:01,549
For that, I shall
reward you...

124
00:11:02,117 --> 00:11:04,119
What do you
wish for...?

125
00:11:04,419 --> 00:11:06,722
{\an1}There is only one
thing, Lord Orochimaru.

126
00:11:06,756 --> 00:11:10,192
Power. Power as
a shinobi...

127
00:11:10,226 --> 00:11:12,061
{\an1}...We wish for nothing
more than that...

128
00:11:12,763 --> 00:11:17,868
{\an1}So it shall be. That's
quite impressive, all
of you...

129
00:11:17,900 --> 00:11:20,738
I commend you
on your choice.

130
00:11:20,772 --> 00:11:25,176
{\an1}Kabuto, be sure to
add each of them
to the sample.

131
00:11:25,209 --> 00:11:27,278
{\an1}I understand, sir.

132
00:11:27,612 --> 00:11:33,050
{\an1}To access the next level
of power within you, you
need a vengeful heart.

133
00:11:33,084 --> 00:11:39,958
{\an4}...possessing an extreme
desire for revenge will
rapidly increase the power
of the Curse Mark...

134
00:11:39,992 --> 00:11:43,263
{\an1}What's the connection
between that and the
Reanimation Jutsu?

135
00:11:43,296 --> 00:11:49,135
{\an4}The emotions your four
learned from overcoming
the dear of death at
that laboratory...

136
00:11:49,169 --> 00:11:53,974
{\an1}...are resentment and
hatred towards me...

137
00:11:54,008 --> 00:11:57,646
{\an1}No, an even stronger
feeling...

138
00:11:57,679 --> 00:12:04,453
{\an4}I'm sure you swore to
get back at me one day,
even if you were killed
in the process...

139
00:12:05,086 --> 00:12:09,991
{\an1}That emotion... When you
can hate someone as
strongly as that...

140
00:12:10,026 --> 00:12:13,496
{\an1}<i>Once you're actually</i>
<i>killed... you take it</i>
<i>with you...</i>

141
00:12:13,529 --> 00:12:16,300
{\an1}<i>...that hatred towards</i>
<i>the one who put you to</i>
<i>death...</i>

142
00:12:16,333 --> 00:12:22,172
{\an4}<i>You die thinking that if</i>
<i>you could be resurrected,</i>
<i>it would be to only seek</i>
<i>revenge...</i>

143
00:12:23,073 --> 00:12:29,681
{\an4}<i>Yes... through the</i>
<i>Reanimation Jutsu, you</i>
<i>will return as ones</i>
<i>seeking vengeance.</i>

144
00:12:29,714 --> 00:12:33,652
{\an1}<i>You will attain power</i>
<i>unlike anything you've</i>
<i>ever had before...</i>

145
00:12:33,686 --> 00:12:39,358
{\an4}<i>The source of your</i>
<i>newfound strength will</i>
<i>be your consuming desire</i>
<i>for vengeance...</i>

146
00:12:39,391 --> 00:12:45,799
{\an1}<i>Embrace that power!</i>
<i>Take pleasure in it!</i>
<i>Revel in its might!</i>

147
00:12:48,368 --> 00:12:53,541
{\an1}Today, just as in the
past, we belong to
Lord Orochimaru!

148
00:12:55,042 --> 00:12:56,477
[gasps]

149
00:12:58,346 --> 00:13:02,751
{\an1}We are Lord Orochimaru's
very own seekers of vengeance!

150
00:13:04,186 --> 00:13:10,860
{\an4}The intense hatred and
resentment that we harbor
towards you allows us to release
the full depths of our power!

151
00:13:10,894 --> 00:13:14,030
{\an1}The way it stands now,
no one can stop us!

152
00:13:14,063 --> 00:13:20,271
{\an7}Don't you even dare to think
of lumping us in with all
those other damn reanimations
you big piece of trash!

153
00:13:25,610 --> 00:13:28,213
Th- thats...

154
00:13:28,246 --> 00:13:32,552
{\an1}What? They were seriously
reanimated only to get
revenge against us?

155
00:13:32,585 --> 00:13:34,687
They're all
insane.

156
00:13:34,720 --> 00:13:39,993
{\an1}If what they said is
true, then they're only
starting to get serious.

157
00:13:42,361 --> 00:13:43,864
Hm.

158
00:14:03,419 --> 00:14:05,321
Ahhhh!

159
00:14:09,426 --> 00:14:11,928
[groans]

160
00:14:12,128 --> 00:14:13,563
{\an1}<i>(Jirobo)</i>
<i>It's too soon...</i>
Huh?

161
00:14:13,597 --> 00:14:17,300
{\an1}You can't quit on
me this early!!

162
00:14:17,702 --> 00:14:20,471
[screams]

163
00:14:35,054 --> 00:14:41,461
{\an1}Fool! Against my improved
Gum Style Spider Thread,
your Gentle Fist is nothing!

164
00:14:42,963 --> 00:14:44,031
[gasp]

165
00:14:47,002 --> 00:14:53,173
{\an5}[evil laugh] Besides!
I've always been better
at grappling than
shooting, anyway!

166
00:14:54,242 --> 00:14:56,012
{\an1}Wolf Fang Over Fang!

167
00:15:01,249 --> 00:15:03,119
Did we get him?

168
00:15:06,890 --> 00:15:10,360
{\an1}Yeah, right! You've
gotta be joking!

169
00:15:11,261 --> 00:15:14,197
{\an1}Like that amount of
power would do any
thing to us!

170
00:15:14,564 --> 00:15:17,167
{\an1}Now, it's our turn!

171
00:15:20,004 --> 00:15:22,340
[gasp]

172
00:15:22,373 --> 00:15:26,078
{\an1}[pleased laughter]
<i>The power of this</i>
<i>Curse Mark is amazing!</i>

173
00:15:26,310 --> 00:15:31,250
{\an4}<i>With this, super</i>
<i>fast cell fusion</i>
<i>and cell division</i>
<i>is now possible!</i>

174
00:15:56,311 --> 00:15:57,312
[gasp]

175
00:15:58,647 --> 00:16:07,858
{\an1}So being bound by
shadows, means stuff
like this is possible?

176
00:16:07,891 --> 00:16:08,926
Argh!

177
00:16:15,033 --> 00:16:16,633
[grunt]

178
00:16:17,035 --> 00:16:21,172
{\an1}You guys are too
weak, you pieces
of trash!!

179
00:16:21,207 --> 00:16:23,109
{\an1}Gimme a sec, I'll
prove you wrong!

180
00:16:23,976 --> 00:16:26,478
{\an1}They've progressed to
a superhuman level!

181
00:16:26,511 --> 00:16:29,148
<i>(Shikamaru)</i>
<i>[laughs]</i>

182
00:16:29,181 --> 00:16:29,915
{\an1}Hm?

183
00:16:31,084 --> 00:16:34,087
All right, then.
Did you get it out
of your system?

184
00:16:35,421 --> 00:16:37,124
{\an1}Don't act so smug.

185
00:16:37,157 --> 00:16:40,427
{\an1}The only reason you're
still here is that we've
been going easy on you!

186
00:16:40,962 --> 00:16:44,397
{\an1}<i>But I'm only barely</i>
<i>holding back my urge</i>
<i>to kill you!</i>

187
00:16:44,899 --> 00:16:47,068
{\an1}Oh yeah? You know
what, about that...

188
00:16:47,101 --> 00:16:49,637
{\an1}Let me go. Come on.
Let me outta here.

189
00:16:49,670 --> 00:16:53,008
{\an1}Boy, you've got some
big balls, I'll give
you that!

190
00:16:53,041 --> 00:16:55,677
{\an1}My hatred just grew
a hundred times!

191
00:16:55,711 --> 00:16:58,982
[♪ flute music]

192
00:17:00,183 --> 00:17:04,788
{\an1}[grunt] So you really
hate me that much, do you?

193
00:17:04,821 --> 00:17:06,322
{\an1}<i>(Tayuya)</i>
<i>Yeah, I do!</i>

194
00:17:07,657 --> 00:17:10,194
{\an1}Why do you insist
on provoking her
so much?

195
00:17:10,227 --> 00:17:11,361
<i>(Shikamaru)</i>
<i>Choji...</i>

196
00:17:11,394 --> 00:17:13,164
{\an3}Huh?

197
00:17:13,197 --> 00:17:17,269
{\an4}Do you remember what we
talked about shortly before
all of us got brought to
this place?

198
00:17:17,301 --> 00:17:18,737
[gasp]

199
00:17:21,173 --> 00:17:25,443
Fortunately for us, HQ
has a strategy for
identifying the fakes.

200
00:17:25,477 --> 00:17:27,546
{\an1}What? They already
came up with a plan?

201
00:17:28,413 --> 00:17:31,717
I do. At least, I
think. What about it?

202
00:17:31,751 --> 00:17:35,122
<i>(Shikamaru)</i>
<i>HQ's strategy is to</i>
<i>utilize Naruto's power!</i>

203
00:17:35,155 --> 00:17:36,757
[gasps]

204
00:17:36,790 --> 00:17:41,762
{\an1}It seems the sensory power
that Naruto now possesses
allows him to sense evil.

205
00:17:41,795 --> 00:17:45,667
{\an1}Not many people know
about it, but if they
don't, they will soon.

206
00:17:45,700 --> 00:17:50,638
{\an4}Because right now, Naruto
is heading to every one of
the battlefields with his
Shadow Clones.

207
00:17:50,672 --> 00:17:52,074
[grunt]

208
00:17:52,107 --> 00:17:53,441
Shikamaru!

209
00:17:53,474 --> 00:17:55,311
{\an1}What are you
rambling on about?

210
00:17:56,545 --> 00:18:01,617
{\an1}[grunt] Sorry, guys.
But this time, I'm really
only going on intuition.

211
00:18:01,650 --> 00:18:03,687
{\an1}I bet it'll happen
soon, though.

212
00:18:03,720 --> 00:18:04,120
{\an3}Huh?

213
00:18:05,755 --> 00:18:08,692
{\an4}<i>(Shikamaru)</i>
<i>This is the third reason</i>
<i>why we don't need to</i>
<i>fight these guys directly.</i>

214
00:18:08,725 --> 00:18:13,064
{\an1}<i>Because knowing him,</i>
<i>he's definitely going</i>
<i>to find this place!</i>

215
00:18:13,297 --> 00:18:15,133
{\an1}That's what I've
been betting on.

216
00:18:16,268 --> 00:18:17,970
[nervous gasps]

217
00:18:21,340 --> 00:18:22,875
Ahhh!

218
00:18:23,309 --> 00:18:24,143
[grunt]

219
00:18:25,078 --> 00:18:27,446
{\an7}Inoichi! You
were right!

220
00:18:27,479 --> 00:18:31,885
{\an7}I went towards a pitch-
black aura of evil, and
I found a giant barrier!

221
00:18:32,253 --> 00:18:34,454
Leave the rest
to us, Naruto.

222
00:18:34,487 --> 00:18:39,026
{\an4}As long as we know where
Shikamaru and the others
are, we can save them.
Right, Shikaku?

223
00:18:39,059 --> 00:18:41,395
<i>(Shikaku)</i>
<i>I leave it up to you...</i>

224
00:18:42,663 --> 00:18:44,232
{\an1}All right! Got it!

225
00:18:45,934 --> 00:18:50,206
{\an4}<i>(Neji)</i>
<i>I see. You kept provoking</i>
<i>them to make it possible for</i>
<i>him to sense their malice.</i>

226
00:18:50,672 --> 00:18:53,441
<i>(Kiba)</i>
<i>You had faith that Naruto</i>
<i>would get what's going on!</i>

227
00:18:53,475 --> 00:18:54,911
<i>(Choji)</i>
<i>Yeah!</i>

228
00:18:55,443 --> 00:18:58,414
There's no doubt
about it, you guys
are really strong...

229
00:18:58,447 --> 00:19:00,750
{\an1}...But you made the
same mistake as you
did the last time.

230
00:19:00,783 --> 00:19:04,221
{\an1}Just like when we faced
you before, we aren't
fighting alone, now.

231
00:19:04,254 --> 00:19:08,226
{\an1}<i>Back then, we had comrades</i>
<i>who rescued us when we were</i>
<i>backed into a corner.</i>

232
00:19:08,259 --> 00:19:13,164
{\an4}<i>And now that we're in</i>
<i>another one, we have</i>
<i>faith that they'll come</i>
<i>to help us once more!</i>

233
00:19:13,197 --> 00:19:17,835
{\an1}<i>We know that as long</i>
<i>as we stand firm,</i>
<i>there's always hope.</i>

234
00:19:17,869 --> 00:19:22,608
{\an4}<i>That's the bond that</i>
<i>exists between true</i>
<i>comrades, and that's</i>
<i>what defeated you guys!</i>

235
00:19:23,642 --> 00:19:27,147
{\an1}The last fight, and
this one as well.

236
00:19:27,180 --> 00:19:30,283
Yeah? Well we
haven't lost yet!

237
00:19:33,387 --> 00:19:39,493
{\an5}But you are about to!
You won't be able to
break or counter this
power! It's impossible!

238
00:19:40,429 --> 00:19:42,029
Shikamaru!

239
00:19:42,063 --> 00:19:43,898
Yeah!

240
00:19:43,932 --> 00:19:45,633
That's good!
We're connected!

241
00:19:45,666 --> 00:19:47,202
<i>Release!</i>

242
00:19:53,242 --> 00:19:54,010
{\an1}[gasp]

243
00:19:56,245 --> 00:19:58,247
Wait! You're--

244
00:19:58,282 --> 00:20:00,016
{\an1}<i>(Kidomaru)</i>
<i>That brat from</i>
<i>last time!</i>

245
00:20:00,049 --> 00:20:03,020
{\an5}<i>(Sakon)</i>
<i>No way! He tore apart</i>
<i>the barrier from the</i>
<i>outside!?</i>

246
00:20:03,053 --> 00:20:07,558
{\an5}<i>(Ukon)</i>
<i>This is bad, Sakon!</i>
<i>If the barrier's broken,</i>
<i>our souls will..</i>

247
00:20:07,591 --> 00:20:12,496
{\an1}So what!? Before that
we can at least get our
revenge on this guy!

248
00:20:16,634 --> 00:20:18,570
[attack cries]

249
00:20:18,603 --> 00:20:22,041
{\an1}Nothing worthwhile is
ever born out of vengeance!

250
00:20:30,017 --> 00:20:34,489
(Sakon)
No! Our... souls...!

251
00:20:39,260 --> 00:20:44,899
{\an1}<i>The influence of the </i>
<i>Curse Mark on the dead's</i>
<i>desire for revenge...</i>

252
00:20:44,933 --> 00:20:48,704
{\an1}<i>Well, at least the</i>
<i>data I collected about</i>
<i>that was worth it.</i>

253
00:20:48,737 --> 00:20:54,210
{\an1}<i>I think that pretty soon</i>
<i>I'll be able to send him</i>
<i>out onto the battlefield...</i>

254
00:20:54,244 --> 00:20:59,316
{\an1}<i>And when that happens, all</i>
<i>of these "opening acts"</i>
<i>will be inconsequential...</i>

255
00:21:01,718 --> 00:21:08,692
[happy sobbing]

256
00:21:09,727 --> 00:21:14,199
{\an7}<i>This time, I was able to</i>
<i>use the enemy's malice to</i>
<i>our advantage...</i>

257
00:21:14,232 --> 00:21:18,538
{\an7}<i>But the malice of war is</i>
<i>spreading like wildfire.</i>

258
00:21:18,570 --> 00:21:20,873
{\an8}<i>I have to put an</i>
<i>end to this, quickly!</i>

259
00:22:57,281 --> 00:22:59,183
<i>(Hinata)</i>
<i>Are you doing all</i>
<i>right now, Neji?</i>

260
00:22:59,216 --> 00:23:02,853
{\an5}<i>(Neji)</i>
<i>My eyes have recovered a</i>
<i>lot, but I still have some</i>
<i>blind spots...</i>

261
00:23:02,886 --> 00:23:07,458
{\an5}<i>(Hinata)</i>
<i>Then rest assured, until</i>
<i>your eyes have healed, I'll</i>
<i>be sure to protect you!</i>

262
00:23:07,492 --> 00:23:09,495
{\an5}<i>(Hinata)</i>
<i>...just as you</i>
<i>protected me back</i>
<i>then...</i>

263
00:23:09,528 --> 00:23:11,197
<i>(Neji)</i>
<i>When I protected you?</i>

264
00:23:11,230 --> 00:23:14,934
<i>(Hinata)</i>
<i>It was when Sasuke</i>
<i>was still in the village.</i>

265
00:23:14,967 --> 00:23:19,705
<i>(Naruto)</i>
<i>Next time on Naruto Shippuden:</i>
<i>"The Heart's Eye."</i>

266
00:23:19,738 --> 00:23:23,476
<i>(Hinata)</i>
<i>I've always wanted to</i>
<i>tell you this... to say...</i>

